The '''lipi''' was a [[Plant/Legends|plant]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Cilpar]]. It was known for its scavenging flowers. [[Throm Loro]] was covered by lipi flowers when [[Elscol Loro]] found him two days after his [[Death/Legends|death]] at the [[Battle of the Cliffs]].

